## The 8 Research Dimensions

1. **Developer Frustration with AI Coding Tools** — Pain points with Claude Code, Cursor, Copilot; quality degradation, cost opacity, lack of pre-build judgment
2. **Spec-Driven Development and PRD Tooling Market** — Landscape of Kiro, Intent, BMAD; gap for adversarial validation before code
3. **x402 Protocol & HTTP Micropayments for AI Agents** — frames.ag, Solana settlement, autonomous agent spending, budget governance gap
4. **Market Validation Tools and Founder Research Pain Points** — 90% startup failure rate, validation tools gap, Validator AI landscape
5. **Agentic Development Workflows and Multi-Agent Orchestration** — Pydantic AI, VoltAgent, Claude Managed Agents; production readiness, cost overruns
6. **Subscription Fatigue and Pay-Per-Use Pricing Models** — $200/mo Claude Code = $1,428/mo at API rates; demand for granular pricing
7. **Competitive Landscape for AI-Powered Product Planning** — ChatPRD, Linear AI, Aha!; gap for single-prompt ICP + PRD + business plan
8. **Non-Developer Founders and Technical Co-Founder Replacement** — 1.2M developer shortage, 94% failure rate for non-technical founders, AI-native dev services

