## ICP in Sharp Focus

**Primary ICP:** Technical founders and senior engineers already paying for Claude Code or Cursor who can build fast but fear building the wrong thing. Willing to pay $9–49 per validation run for shareable, repo-native artifacts.

**Secondary ICP:** Non-technical founders who understand their market but cannot bridge the gap to technical execution. Need a structured artifact (PRD + business plan + ICP + competitive landscape) to hand to a developer or AI agent.

